TERMINATION

This license is effective until terminated. Your rights under this license will
be terminated immediately if you:
- Violate the revenue threshold or hosted service restriction
- Attempt circumvention or anti-circumvention violations
- Remove or alter copyright notices
- Refuse to provide audit information when reasonably requested
- Fail to attribute SENTINEL when required

Upon termination, you must:
- Cease all use of SENTINEL
- Delete all copies in your possession or control
- Cease offering any service based on SENTINEL to third parties

The restrictions on hosted services, commercial derivatives, sublicensing, and
anti-circumvention survive termination and remain binding perpetually.

